title: Is the Porsche 911 GT3 The Best Sports Car Ever Built? - AFTER/DRIVE
description:
The Porsche 911 GT3 has always been the Porsche to buy if you really love driving. The newest model is a marvel of technology, but is it still a true driver's car? Discuss.

With Zac Moseley and Mike Prichinello from Classic Car Club Manhattan.
http://www.classiccarclubmanhattan.com
